===Hardware specification=== *CPU: ''[[NXP]]'' LS1023A @1.0GHz :Dual Core ARM (Cortex-A53) *Memory: 2GB (DDR4) SDRAM *Storage: 4MB (SPI) Flash, 4GB (eMMC) *Wi-Fi: [[Qualcomm Atheros]] QCA9880 (802.11abgn/ac) *Network: 5x GbE ports *USB: 2x USB 3.0 ports *Power: 12V/2.5A via barrel
